body:
#### PR description:

* resolves #30539
* resolves issue reported by @srimanob w/ missing ESProducers, and adds TestOldDigiProdLike workflow (which corresponds to the commands that produced the issue)
* puts D49 ProdLike workflow in IB tests
* several minor fixes for L1T issues observed while running workflows

Will backport to 11_1_X.

#### PR validation:

Ran relevant workflows: 20634.99, 23234.0, 23234.1001, 23234.1002, 23234.21
title: Fix L1T bugs and add workflows
